column3: That log you link is unfortunate. Concept ACK.\n
When / why did this start happening; did something change in the Cirrus?

> When / why did this start happening; did something change in the Cirrus?

As for now, the latest Cirrus logs are available for ce0913148b687310f2933397d0bbe4bd014c178e (2021-08-10), and CI behavior has not been changed since then.

I suspect, it was a flaw in 3c2478c38522c176e81befd4d991a259b09be063 (#20697), which remained unnoticed as no one cares about _successful_ lint task logs :)\
